ZH: 我住在楼上。
EN: I live upstairs in the building.

ZH: 这座楼已经建了五年了。
EN: This building has been built for five years.

ZH: 我的办公室在这座楼的22楼。
EN: My office is on the 22nd floor of this building.

ZH: 这幢楼的外观设计很独特。
EN: The architecture design of this building is very unique.

ZH: 那座楼太高了，我不敢上去。
EN: That building is too tall, I dare not go up.

ZH: 请将包裹送到这座楼的门口。
EN: Please deliver the package to the entrance of this building.

ZH: 外面下雨了，我在楼下等你。
EN: It's raining outside, I'll wait for you downstairs.

ZH: 那座楼是这个城市的地标。
EN: That building is a landmark of this city.

ZH: 昨天我们在楼顶看到了日出。
EN: Yesterday we saw the sunrise from the rooftop.

ZH: 我从楼梯上摔了下来，摔伤了腿。
EN: I fell down the stairs from the building and hurt my leg.

ZH: 这幢楼已经形同废墟，无人居住。
EN: This building has become a ruin, no one lives there.

ZH: 爬楼梯可以锻炼你的腿部肌肉。
EN: Climbing stairs can exercise your leg muscles.

ZH: 这座楼在地震中倒塌了。
EN: This building collapsed in the earthquake.

ZH: 我独自走出楼宇，踏上了新的征程。
EN: I walked out of the building alone and embarked on a new journey.

ZH: 别在楼道里乱扔垃圾。
EN: Don't throw trash in the hallway.

ZH: 那家公司租用了整栋楼来办公。
EN: That company rented the entire building for office use.

ZH: 在楼里走廊里，传来一阵阵欢笑声。
EN: Laughter echoed through the halls of the building.

ZH: 这座楼前后手脚之劳，耗费了无数时间和金钱。
EN: It took countless time and money to build this building.

ZH: 在楼顶平台上俯瞰整个城市，风景宜人。
EN: The view from the rooftop terrace overlooking the entire city is delightful.

ZH: 他的房间在游泳池边的一栋楼里。
EN: His room is in a building next to the swimming pool.
